type: api
title: Post echo
description: Send a JSON body to the echo endpoint using an environment-based URL and env accessors
url: <<e:base_url>>/echo
method: post
format: json
headers:
  X-Custom: e:custom_header
  X-Custom-Prefix: <<e:custom_header[0:5]>>
body:
  name: Multimeter
  message: Hello from <<e:base_url[0:8]>>
